Apeface roared to a stop, and in mid-air transformed into his gorrilla
mode. On his way down, he flipped twice in mid air, and then landed,
quickly heading into the tower on all fours. Once inside he transformed.
"Did you get my message boss?" Asked Apeface, he saluted as soon as he
entered.
